snippet.textDisplay:
Kudos to Sona, Rituraj and the entire team of Coke Studio, India for this marvellous effort of putting up the song in such forum without losing the essence of the original. Its a pity that so many people were against the way the song was presented. I guess they are less familiar with the word modernization and digitization of music. 
By the way, I am from Sambalpur, Odisha - The place were this song was born.
